snippet.textDisplay:
اگر کسی گانے کی روح نکالنی ہو تو اسے کوک سٹوڈیو میں گایا جائے۔
مجھے آج تک کوک سٹوڈیو نے متاثر نہیں کیا۔ بلکہ جب کبھی کسی اچھے گلوکار کے دھوکے میں کوک سٹوڈیو کے کسی کلپ پر کلک کر دیا تو اس گلوگار پر رحم آیا کر یہ کوک سٹوڈیو کے چکر میں کیسے آیا گیا۔ 
کوک سٹوڈیو اپنی اس مردہ موسیقی کو چھپانے کے لیے وڈیو کا سہارا لیتا ہے۔ تاکہ سننے والے کا توجہ انتہائی فضول اور گانے کی دھن سے متضاد میوزک پر نہ جائے۔ 
عابدہ پروین، سجاد علی اور راحت فتح علی خان، ابرارالحق اور ان جیسے بڑے اور سنجیدہ گلوکاروں کو کوک سٹوڈیو سے پرہیز کرنا چاہیئے۔  کوک سٹوڈیو ان گلوکاروں کے اپنے اصلی اور سپر ہٹ گانوں کا بھی حشر کر دے گا۔
یہی وجہ ہے کہ کوک سٹوڈیو کا میوزک کبھی یو ٹیوب سے باہر نہیں نکل سکا۔

snippet.textDisplay:
Music knows no boundaries, Good to hear from all the folks listed under ,appeasing the artist, more importantly, words count when there are one against other as considered on political and many other grounds but the atmosphere here is completely different, mesmerizing and compelling to make one think of how our lives are influenced by the music and talents performed from both the side, good to have coke studios as a platform for such genuine artists who aren't wasting their talents in stupid film industries. I've almost all the Coke Studio Sessions both from India and Pakistan, I certainly have it in my personal collection and always keep it intact and handy, I've like all the major performances from both the lands but Coke Studio Sessons 7, especially with all the distinguished artist performing on the musical scores are just awesome and great to watch and eventually listen to.

Thanks to Coke Studios, you're doing a great job, I myself, being a musician would definitely like to see more of this in the future to come and I'll always be expecting more out of it and above all, a huge thank to Youtube - for you guys at youtube... I'm sorry, I do not have words to express my gratitude.

What feels great hear is all the people leaving great comments for the artists and music performed and I'd like to say to all of them who have commented here, 'May god bless you all', if this is what both the countries have in common, we're blessed.

Great job Coke Studio Pakistan. Keep it up.

snippet.textDisplay: What a wonderful fusion of traditional and contemporary musical form. First and foremost congratulations to Humera Channa and Abbas Ali Khan and accompanying musicians. Then to Bilal Maqsood and Faisal Kapadia for ably filling Rohail Hyatt's shoes. Bless you all for producing this hauntingly beautiful piece. We have every reason to be proud of our most wonderful musical heritage. Thank you.
